				<td rowspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" style="text-align: justify;" width="100%" valign=top>
				<P><STRONG>Being a paladin when ever I consider a new item ( i.e. an possible upgrade) I&nbsp; first see how they improve my HP and AC. I go by the ratio of 4 HP == 1 AC.&nbsp; I next look to see if it has shielding or avoidance ( as I am not maxxed out on those yet). &nbsp;After that I check the resistances.&nbsp; My stats are all maxxed so I do not look to those, but a lower levels I checked STR, STA, WIS, DEX, AGI ( in that order).. Special focus goodies I see if I have them on another item. Always looking for those that will allow me to tank that much longer, or heal that much better.. </STRONG></P>
				
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=913576
