esist:</FONT> average<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Disease Resist:</FONT> above average<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Poison Resist:</FONT> above average<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Magic Resist:</FONT> below average<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Fire Resist:</FONT> average<BR>I am a resist freak.&nbsp; Every enchanter I talk to has Posion as thier lowest resist even with Dead Man Floating on. Disease is always a close 2nd.&nbsp; Oddly ot my current gear level however Fire is suddenly become my 2nd worse.&nbsp; Now sure what changed.<BR>&nbsp;<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Attack:</FONT> Nice for farming Greens/lt blue.&nbsp; Not game breaking<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Delay:</FONT> Nice for farming Greens/lt blue.&nbsp; Not game breaking<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Damage:</FONT> Nice for farming Greens/lt blue.&nbsp; Not game breaking<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Range:</FONT> zero<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Haste:</FONT> Nice for farming Greens/lt blue.&nbsp; Not game breaking<BR>&nbsp;<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Combat Effects:</FONT> Nice for farming Greens/lt blue.&nbsp; Not game breaking<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Shielding:</FONT> VERY important and hard to Cap, IMPOSSIBLE to cap at my CoA level.&nbsp; I place a higher importance on Shielding than Avoidance only becasue it is hard to cap.&nbsp; Avoidance is more important to have but WAY easier to cap.<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Stun Resist:</FONT> Very important. The differnce between a wipe and a heroic save (or even locking down a simple single add) may be not getting stunned.<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Strikethrough:</FONT> zero, I don't melee any mobe this is an issue on.<BR><FONT color=#ff0000>Spell Shield:</FONT> Very important to survive AE's on raids.&nbsp; However Our runes make this less important than other classes.</P>
