 tick on a high end gear chanter over a naked one.&nbsp; No foci effects debuffs or buffs other than duration which REALLY doesn't matter all that much.&nbsp; But adding a Foci that effects runes by X% would start to make so gear difference between chanters, in my humble opinion anyway.</P><p>Message Edited by Breez_Bayou on <span class=date_text>07-06-2006</span> <span class=time_text>12:44 PM</span>
				
